io.codeleaf.config.spec

Interface Specification

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<Specification.Setting>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DecoratedSpecification, MapSpecification

    public interface Specification
extends Iterable<Specification.Setting>
    This represents a specification. A specification consists of a collection of settings. Each setting has a field, modeled as a List<String>, and a value, modeled as a Object.
    Since:
    0.1.0
    Author:
    tvburger@gmail.com
